'''Fatima Meer''' (12 Phato 1928 - 12 Hlakubele 2010) e ne e le sengoli sa Afrika Boroa, mosuoe, mongoli oa skrini, le molaoli ea hlahelletseng oa khahlano e khethollo. O belegetswe Grey Street,Durban . ke morwedi wa Moosa Meer le Rachel Farrel ,ke ngwana wa bobedi go bana ba seswai . Mmagwe be ele tshiwana a sena batswadi a dula legae la bana ba ditshiwana ,tatagwe o belegetswe surat ,gurat .Yo fatima meer otsere ngwaga yunibesithing ya WIts a be a ba leloko la la Progressive forum ,o ile a thoma go ruta batho babagolo ka bobeyelo bja sefatanaga bja tatagwe ka ngwaga wa 1940 .Mmereko wa gagwe wa dipolotiki o thomile ge anale mengwaga ye lesome supa a le sekolong se se phagamego . Fatima Meer e be ele yo mongwe wa diboledi tse kgolo kopanong yeo e bego e swerwe  go lwesa mmuso gore o  seke wa tsebisa molao o moswa wa GROUP AREAS ACT . Meer le Dr Goonam e be ele basadi ba mathomo go kgethwa goba bagolo ba Natal Indian Congress .O thome  Durban and District Women's League ,pele ga dintwa tsa 1949 tseo di bego di thoma ke makgowa go kgaogantsha makula le bathobaso bao ba bego ba berekisana mmogo go tsa dipolotiki bae pitsa ANC le NIC . E  be le sekeretari  le Betha Mkhize ,mopresidente wa ANC WOMEN'S LEAGUE bjalo ka modulasetulo .E be ele mokgatlo wa mathomo nageng ya rena yeo makula le bathobaso ba bilego ngata e tee .Mokgatlo wo o tsere mathata sebakeng sa basadi ba maAfrika Borwa bao ba bego ba hloriswa ka lebaka la dipasa ba be ba swariwa ,ya ba ya swara lesolo magareng ga makula go emisa go arogantshwa ga ma Afrika Borwa le makula.
